                        p.time 2:00 am
                        p.info Late night snack is served.
                    .entry
                        p.time 8:00 am
                        p.info Breakfast is served.
                    .entry
                        p.time 12:00 pm
                        p.info Lunch is served.
                    .entry
                        p.time 6:00 pm
                        p.info Dinner is served.
                    h4 Sunday, March 8th
                    .entry
